{"type": "article", "id": 28981, "title": "可以听音乐的杯子", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120726XNVK4mL7Mglo5cqe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果说有谁会在喝水时脑洞大开，可能指的就是来自 <a href=\"https://www.dubgear.com/\">Dubgear</a> 的设计师了，他们最新的产品是一个既能倒出饮料又能流淌出音乐的杯子 Dubstein。它的左右两侧各有一对突出的喇叭，通过蓝牙功能与设备相连后就可以边喝饮料边享受音乐了。Dubstein 自带可拆卸的保温杯，也可以替换成清凉的罐装饮料或者啤酒。采用人体工程学设计的把手上是一些操控按钮，只要使用大拇指轻轻按下即可。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.dubgear.com/products/dubstein\">购买链接</a>，售价为 100.46 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120724uNGy8xlFjRCO6bke.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41060291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120724WJEuYmLNsDZMaPfp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40970072\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120724LyzJwDWr5gIqoGMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41054809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120725JmHS9zQ61Wy5pDfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}